<L>Sit, with his diademe on heade,</L>
<L>The Sonne, &s;hinende in his carte:</L>
<L>And for to lead him &s;withe<NOTE N="z" PLACE="foot">Swift.</NOTE> and &s;marte,</L>
<L>After the bright dai&egrave;s lawe,</L>
<L>There ben ordained for to drawe</L>
<L>Four hors his chare, and him withall,</L>
<L>Whereoff the names tell I &s;hall:</L>
<L>Eritheus the fir&s;t is hote <NOTE N="a" PLACE="foot">Named.</NOTE>,</L>
