<L>They trompyd up full meryly,</L>
<L>The grete battell to gederes &yogh;ed <NOTE N="u" PLACE="foot">This is Milton's "Together ru&s;h'd both battles main."</NOTE>;</L>
<L>Our archorys<NOTE N="w" PLACE="foot">Archers.</NOTE> theiy &s;chot ful hartely,</L>
<L>They made the Frenche men fa&s;te to blede,</L>
