<L>Thenn dydd&s;t thou furyou&s;e &s;tonde,</L>
<L>And bie thie brondeous honde</L>
<L>Bee&s;prengedd all the mees with gore.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>Drawne bie thyne anlace felle <NOTE N="l" PLACE="foot">Sword.</NOTE>,</L>
<L>Downe to the depthe of helle,</L>
