<LG>
<PB N="149" REF="155">
<L>Oh! thou, where'er (thie bones att re&s;te)</L>
<L>Thie &s;pryte to haunt delyghteth be&s;te,</L>
<L>Whytherr upponn the bloude-embrewedd pleyne<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter"></L>
<L>Orr whare thou kenn&s;t fromme farre</L>
<L>The dy&s;malle crie of warre,</L>
<L>Orr &s;ee&s;te &s;omme mountayne made of cor&s;e of &s;leyne:</L>
</LG>
<LG>
