<P>Pag. 30. to Not. ^d. ADD, <Q REND="inline">"In the &s;ame &s;tile, as it is mani|fe&s;tly of the &s;ame antiquity, the following little de&s;criptive &s;ong, on the Approach of Summer, de&s;erves notice. MSS. HARL. 978. f. 5.</Q></P>
