<P>Pag. 113. ADD to Not. ^i. <Q REND="inline">"On a review of this pa&s;&s;age in Hoveden, it appears to have been William bi&s;hop of Ely, chancellor to king Richard the fir&s;t, who thus invited min&s;trels
